ux</strong>, adopted in educational and entrepreneurial communities.</div><div><br></div><div>Skilled in designing <strong>acceleration pathways</strong>, facilitating <strong>workshops and bootcamps</strong>, mentoring \100+ founders, and leading national innovation initiatives. Passionate about enabling mission-driven entrepreneurs through <strong>systems thinking</strong>, <strong>qualitative research</strong>, and <strong>impact-focused program design</strong>.</div>"\}],"name":"","record":"SummarySection","showTitle":true},{"__t":"ExperienceSection","column":0,"enabled":true,"height":28,"items":[{"dateRange":{"fromMonth":null,"fromYear":2025,"isOngoing":true,"ongoingText":"","record":"DateRange","toMonth":null,"toYear\":null},"table":{"cols":2,"record":"TableItem","rows":[["<b>Project name</b>","<b>Description</b>"],["",""]]},"height":275,"id":"njtk8mriv6","record":"ExperienceItem","alignment":"justify","bullets":["Led Revenue Operations and Growth strategy, aligning m\arketing, sales, and operations into a <b>unified revenue engine</b>.","Designed and implemented <b>end-to-end revenue funnels</b>, integrating acquisition, lead validation, lifecycle management, and pipeline governance within HubSpot.","<b>Structured </b\>the<b> commercial tech stack</b>: Meta Ads acquisition, automated lead ingestion and qualification via Make, CRM governance, and WhatsApp integration for follow-up acceleration.","Reduced lead friction and improved speed-to-contact through automation wor\kflows and standardized lead status architecture.","Built revenue visibility frameworks enabling data-driven decision-making across founder and commercial leadership teams.","<b>Translated growth strategy into executable processes</b>, balancing rapid exp\erimentation with operational control and responsible scaling.","Established <b>RevOps governance practices </b>connecting demand generation, sales execution, and revenue forecasting."],"companyLogo":"https://enhancv.s3.amazonaws.com/co